This paper is about Open Neural Network Exchange (ONNX), which is a format for representing AI models. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper presents an automatic unit test generator, which involves software engineering and programming language concepts, making it relevant to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-categories.
